Developer Terms of Use
des:
Wake up with Sing 2!

Set the Sing 2 Alarm Tone as a wake-up alarm, a reminder, or to hear your favorite movie moments.

Just say, “Alexa, wake me up at 8 AM with the Sing 2 Alarm tone!” or “Alexa, set an alarm for 7 AM to the Sing 2 alarm tone!” and you’ll be laughing with Buster Moon, Mrs. Crawly, Porscha, and other favorite characters in no time.

And don’t forget, you can enjoy the film at home now!
